</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Frederik Pohl</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="hatnote">This article is about the writer and editor.  For the writer on exploration, see <a href="/wiki/Frederick_J._Pohl" title="Frederick J. Pohl">Frederick J. Pohl</a>.</div>
